---
/**
 * storage-engines · storage-engines-fundamentals · Figure 8 — Level 8, the
 * schema-evolution compatibility rules and the one fatal rule.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source page (figure + svg + figcaption), including
 * the inline <tspan font-family="ui-monospace">. This figure references no
 * markers, so it needs no local <defs>.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 560 150"
        role="img"
        aria-label="The compatibility rules: optional new fields, stable tag numbers, never reuse a retired tag"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="280"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">the rules that preserve both directions</text
            >
            <g font-size="9.5">
                <rect x="20" y="32" width="250" height="26" rx="6" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
                ></rect><text x="30" y="49" fill="#244a2e"
                    >new field optional / default → backward OK</text
                >
                <rect x="20" y="64" width="250" height="26" rx="6" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
                ></rect><text x="30" y="81" fill="#244a2e">unknown tag is skipped → forward OK</text
                >
                <rect x="20" y="96" width="250" height="26" rx="6" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
                ></rect><text x="30" y="113" fill="#244a2e"
                    >identify by stable tag #, rename freely</text
                >
            </g>
            <rect x="300" y="44" width="246" height="64" rx="8" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="423"
                y="66"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a2218">the one fatal rule</text
            >
            <text x="423" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#7a2218"
                >never reuse a retired tag #</text
            >
            <text x="423" y="100" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >→ old code silently misreads the new field</text
            >
            <text x="280" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >proto3 dropped <tspan font-family="ui-monospace">required</tspan> entirely — it's a forward-compat
                landmine</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Protobuf/Thrift identify fields by integer tag; Avro carries no per-field id and resolves
        writer-vs-reader schemas by name.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
